This is a single-center, prospective, randomized, double blind, placebo control study.

 The aim of this study is to assess the effect of fish oil capsules on pain intensity and postoperative analgesics consumption in patients after knee replacement surgery.

 The study population will be adult are referred for knee replacement surgery due to osteoarthritis of the knee.

